const UserFeedback =[
  {
    "id" : 1,
    "userName" : "John",
    "imgsrc" : "/images/users/img1.jpg",

              "SkyCruise.com, it is fast, easy and I had good customer support"
  },
  {
    "id" : 2,
    "userName" : "Sandy",
    "imgsrc" : "/images/users/img2.jpg",
    "text" : "I use SkyCruise.com ALL The Time! It is the BEST! I have"+
             "never had any problems. I have never been"+
              "disappointed! Keep Up the Great Customer Service!"
  },
  {
    "id" : 3,
    "userName" : "Camila",
    "imgsrc" : "/images/users/img3.jpg",
    "text" :  "We use them a lot, we always cross check the hotel pictures"+

  },
  {
    "id" : 4,

    "userName" : "Andrew",
    "imgsrc" : "/images/users/img5.jpg",

  {
    "id" : 6,
    "userName" : "Joelle",
    "imgsrc" : "/images/users/img6.jpg",
    "text" : "I often use it to plan my stay in advice. It has great prices"+
